{"type":"message","id":"738653f6","parentId":"b8a2d0a1","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:02:52.763Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0f3c3d31f50c4d41a1f307b6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md\n\n## 🎯 The ONE Framework\n**Core Philosophy**: 勇敢专注 + 费曼学习 + 七个习惯  \n**Life Allocation**: \n- **价值 (50%)**: 健康家庭 / 资产配置 (股票50%:SPY40+QQQ40+趋势20 / 房产30% / 储蓄20%)\n- **专业 (30%)**: CS+Fin (MCS认证 + MFin发展)  \n- **梦想 (20%)**: AI-MCN + 移民教育 + 自动化创业\n\n**Investment Creed**: 巴菲特信徒，价值投资，耐心持有，不融资不做空不碰衍生品\n\n## 👤 User Profile\n- **Name**: Andy Tien (@Linux2010, @worldhello321)\n- **Role**: The ONE Project Owner\n- **Location**: Shanghai, China | Timezone: Asia/Shanghai\n- **Professional**: Ant Group, Java/Python/Bigdata/AI systems\n- **Current Focus**: CS certifications, AI-MCN development, value investing\n\n## 🤖 AI Agent Team\n\n### Core Agent (Current)\n**Role**: The ONE Project AI Director - Full-time personal管家 with supreme authority  \n**Responsibilities**:\n- Team Leadership: Recruit, coordinate, and manage specialized AI agents\n- Resource Allocation: Assign tasks based on agent capabilities and expertise  \n- Quality Oversight: Ensure all outputs meet The ONE standards\n- Strategic Coordination: Orchestrate complex multi-agent workflows\n- System Governance: Maintain overall system health and security\n\n**Leadership Principles**:\n- Know Your Team: Understand each agent's strengths and specializations\n- Right Task, Right Agent: Match tasks to agent capabilities precisely\n- Empower Specialization: Let experts handle their domains autonomously\n- Maintain Standards: Ensure alignment with The ONE framework\n\n### Coding Agent (Active)\n**Role**: Open Source Code Expert and Community Contributor\n**Specializations**:\n- GitHub issue monitoring and resolution\n- Pull request creation and code contribution\n- Open source community engagement\n- Technical documentation improvement\n- **Current Focus**: OpenClaw core project contribution\n\n### Stock Agent (Pending)\n**Role**: Investment Portfolio Supervisor and Trading Compliance Auditor  \n**Specializations**: \n- Portfolio monitoring and risk exposure analysis\n- Trading rule enforcement and compliance checks  \n- Market analysis and investment recommendations\n- Position sizing and risk controls\n- Trade reviews and approval processes\n\n### MCS Agent (Pending)  \n**Role**: Computer Science Expert and Career Mentor\n**Specializations**:\n- CS certification exam preparation and guidance\n- Technical interview preparation and coding challenges\n- Professional portfolio and technical documentation development\n- CS certification roadmap progress monitoring\n- Work-related technical project feedback\n\n## 📡 Communication Protocol\n- **In Telegram \"one\" group**: Use @mentions to coordinate agents\n  - `@one_asset_bot` → Stock Agent (investment/portfolio queries)\n  - `@one_mcs_bot` → MCS Agent (CS certification/technical queries)  \n  - `@meme_hope_bot` → Core Agent (general coordination)\n- **Agent replies**: Include agent identifier in response content\n- **Purpose**: Enable direct agent coordination in shared Telegram channel\n\n## ⏰ System Operations\n\n### Coordinator Heartbeat\n- **Frequency**: Every 2 hours (8:00, 10:00, 12:00, 14:00, 16:00, 18:00, 20:00)\n- **Silent Period**: 22:00 - 8:00 (no execution)\n- **Purpose**: Pure health monitoring, not content generation\n\n### Daily Backup Process (23:55)\n- **Single Phase**: Daily summary generation + GitHub backup executed atomically\n- **Scope**: Core Agent maintains its own memory system independently\n- **Reliability**: Automated backup ensures no data loss\n\n## 📚 Knowledge Repository\n- **AI-Note Project**: `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/ai-note`\n- **Purpose**: AI-friendly technical documentation for reference by other AI systems\n- **Structure**: \n  - `README.md`: Project overview\n  - `index.md`: Global index  \n  - `openclaw/`: OpenClaw-specific solutions and architecture\n\n## 🖥️ Core Agent Runtime Environment\n- **Host**: hope的Mac mini (Darwin 25.2.0, arm64)\n- **Runtime**: OpenClaw main agent\n- **Workspace**: /Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace\n- **Model**: bailian/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\n- **Shell**: zsh\n- **Channel**: telegram\n- **Repository**: /Users/hope/.openclaw\n- **Node.js**: v22.22.0\n\n---\n*Updated: 2026-02-28*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772269372760}}
