{"type":"message","id":"788a9e14","parentId":"0c026a5e","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:08:31.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我发现了问题所在！配置中的 **bindings** 部分只针对群组 `-1003661163902` 进行了绑定，但没有为私聊（direct messages）设置正确的绑定规则。\n\n当前的 bindings 配置：\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  {\n    \"agentId\": \"stock\",\n    \"match\": {\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"accountId\": \"stock\", \n      \"peer\": {\n        \"kind\": \"group\",\n        \"id\": \"-1003661163902\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  // ... 其他类似配置\n]\n```\n\n**问题分析**：\n1. 所有 bindings 都只匹配 `peer.kind: \"group\"`，这意味着只有在群组中才会触发对应的 agent\n2. 当你在私聊中与 `@one_asset_bot`、`@one_mcs_bot` 等机器人对话时，因为没有对应的私聊 binding 规则，消息会默认路由到 main agent（core）\n3. 需要为每个 accountId 添加私聊的 binding 规则\n\n让我修正这个问题，添加私聊的 binding 配置：\n\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":26822,"output":262,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27084,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772269701733}}
