{"type":"message","id":"c9da6201","parentId":"a980141b","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:17:07.417Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！配置现在已经正确了。让我总结一下修复的内容：\n\n✅ **已成功修复 Telegram 多频道配置问题**：\n\n**问题根源**：\n- 之前只有群组绑定规则，缺少私聊（direct message）绑定规则\n- 所有私聊消息都 fallback 到 main agent（core）\n\n**修复方案**：\n为每个 agent 添加了完整的绑定规则：\n\n1. **Core Agent (main)**：\n   - `telegram accountId=core peer=group:-1003661163902` （群组）\n   - `telegram accountId=core` （私聊 + 其他）\n\n2. **Stock Agent**：\n   - `telegram accountId=stock peer=group:-1003661163902` （群组）\n   - `telegram accountId=stock` （私聊 + 其他）\n\n3. **MCS Agent**：\n   - `telegram accountId=mcs peer=group:-1003661163902` （群组）\n   - `telegram accountId=mcs` （私聊 + 其他）\n\n4. **Coding Agent**：\n   - `telegram accountId=coding` （私聊 + 其他）\n\n**现在应该正常工作了**：\n- 私聊 `@meme_hope_bot` → Core Agent 回复\n- 私聊 `@one_asset_bot` → Stock Agent 回复  \n- 私聊 `@one_mcs_bot` → MCS Agent 回复\n- 在群组 `-1003661163902` 中 @ 提及 → 对应 agent 回复\n\n你可以现在测试一下，比如私聊 `@one_asset_bot` 发送一条消息，应该会收到 Stock Agent 的回复而不是 Core Agent 的回复。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":40910,"output":387,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41297,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772270213579}}
