penclaw/agents/stock/workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/stock/agent\n  Model: bailian/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\n  Routing rules: 2\n  Routing rules:\n    - telegram accountId=stock peer=group:-1003661163902\n    - telegram accountId=stock\n- mcs\n  Identity: 💻 MCS Agent (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/agents/mcs/workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/mcs/agent\n  Model: bailian/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\n  Routing rules: 2\n  Routing rules:\n    - telegram accountId=mcs peer=group:-1003661163902\n    - telegram accountId=mcs\n- coding\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/agents/coding/workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/coding/agent\n  Model: bailian/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\n  Routing rules: 2\n  Routing rules:\n    - telegram accountId=coding\n    - telegram accountId=coding peer=group:-1003661163902\nRouting rules map channel/account/peer to an agent. Use --bindings for full rules.\nChannel status reflects local config/creds. For live health: openclaw channels status --probe.","cwd":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772270652405}}
{"type":"message","id":"54c30b8d","parentId":"c840c6c7","timestamp":"2026-02-28T09:24:24.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **完美！现在完全配置正确了！**\n\n**最终的 Telegram 多频道配置**：\n\n1. **Core Agent (main)**：\n   - 私聊 `@meme_hope_bot` → Core Agent 回复\n   - 群组 `-1003661163902` 中 @core → Core Agent 回复\n\n2. **Stock Agent**：\n   - 私聊 `@one_asset_bot` → Stock Agent 回复  \n   - 群组 `-1003661163902` 中 @one_asset_bot → Stock Agent 回复\n\n3. **MCS Agent**：\n   - 私聊 `@one_mcs_bot` → MCS Agent 回复\n   - 群组 `-1003661163902` 中 @one_mcs_bot → MCS Agent 回复\n\n4. **Coding Agent**：\n   - 私聊 `@coding_bot` → Coding Agent 回复\n   - 群组 `-1003661163902` 中 @coding_bot → Coding Agent 回复\n\n**所有 agent 现在都有完整的绑定规则**（私聊 + 群组），不会再出现所有消息都被 Core Agent 处理的问题了。\n\n你可以现在测试任意一个 bot 的私聊或群组 @ 提及，都会得到对应 agent 的正确回复！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":44618,"output":314,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44932,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772270652406}}
